Node:	touch (Speech response to taps/pats on the should)
Input:
	
Config:
	struct touch { unit8 addr, uint16 pressure }
Output:
	None
Steps:
	Initialization: begin subscribing to tpc_touch (10Hz)
	1. if one or more touch sensors register a tap/pat then:
		(a) send request to srv_speaker ("Thank you")
